Qv9Ggg8tyEA.keywords: Harry Hermione Goodbye lullabyHHr  Goodbye HarmonyThe Story of Friendship, Love and Sacrifice that all of us had witnessed growing up. This video is my way of coming into terms with one of the biggest disappointment in my life which is the Harry and Hermione Pairing not going beyond what is platonic. But since the HHr shipper in me prevails, I pooled all the Deathly Hallows clip I can find all over youtube and made a story line around it and I came up with this Ron left despite Hermione's pleas. In her loneliness, Harry comforts her. And in this moment of weakness, they created a life. A life, that despite hesitance, Hermione was willing to raise with Harry, as she accepts his offer of marriage. And at that moment, Harry promises to provide Hermione and their future family a happy life. Hermione tells him that she is happy but her emotions shows other wise. Just when everything was to be well, Ron shows up and tells Hermione how he truly feels about her. Hermione doesn't react and Harry, although bothered with Ron's reappearance assures himself that he and Hermione still have their future together because of the baby. When Death Eaters attack however, Hermione is captured and tortured. In the whole ordeal, she loses the baby. Harry sits devastated but as he looks back on everything, he stands firm in his decision to marry Hermione because he was in love with her. When he tells her this, she does not give him the reply he wanted from her. Instead, she runs out and Harry, well, he could only stand from a distance and watch, as Hermione chooses Ron over him. "And. For a moment. I thought that she chose me. But she didn't." Seeing Hermione with Ron was something that he could not bare, so he turns and leaves. "And so I said. Goodbye." I wrote this because I detest the idea that Harry and Hermione don't even react negatively or even show any tinge of jealousy whenever the other shows affection to their Canon Pairs. I wanted to believe that Harry and Hermione had gone through something so deep and so life changing that it pains them to be together. And, that in their desperation to escape what they had gone through, decided to accept other people's love instead of each other' s. P. S. Seriously, while editing this video and going over scenes when Ron enters the picture, I was taken aback as to how much I wanted to remove his SMUG of a face from his neck. Honestly, Ron and Hermione NOT A VERY GOODLOOKING COUPLE. GOD! NOT IN A MILLION YEARS. First Place in Best Emotion Harry Potter Epic Contest Londonexplore101

Stampys Skyblock Island Stampys Channel  Minecraft Minecraft is focused on creativity and building, allowing players to build constructions out of textured cubes in a 3D world. Gameplay in its commercial release has two principal modes Survival, which requires players to acquire resources themselves and maintain their health and hunger and Creative, where the player has an unlimited supply of resources, the ability to fly, and no concept of health or hunger. A third gameplay mode, named Hardcore, is essentially the same as Survival, but the difficulty is locked on the hardest setting and respawning is disabled, forcing the player to delete his or her world upon death. An outdated Classic version is also available for free, although it is no longer being developed. Creative Minecraft resembles Classic, but with many more features.
